reviews.text: Good place was great food
Always good food. Pigeon! Busy and noisy.
Dim Sum is good, try their sesame paste bun (麻蓉包)

Really great food, perfect for a large family gathering or work event. They have private function rooms with a PA system that can accommodate 100 plus people. We go here for our work Spring Dinner every year and it doesn't disappoint. They have some unique dishes mixed in with the classics. Probably not ideal for English only customers but if you have local pals or you're feeling adventurous it's a great option.
Impressive Taipo local old tea restaurant. Good for afternoon dimsum with reasonable price.

result.adr_address: 香港大埔運頭街12-18號美華大廈2-3樓
result.formatted_address: 香港大埔運頭街12-18號美華大廈2-3樓
result.name: 大日子酒家

reviews.text:
照樣人多嘈雜，中擋格調，出品亦過得去。價錢可以。
由於附近未有中式酒樓（最近都要去到火車站商場內），中午飲茶經常爆滿，晚飯靜啲。
點心很好食！可惜喺搭枱區冷氣足！可否叫冷氣師傅洗吓風口，情況應該可以改善！！！

一個字「差」
野食一般，服務態度其差
完全熟客優先。
都算，一邊食野一邊同你掃地，重點係個地係地氈，一掃D塵多到呢...
佢樓面咁嘅衛生情況，可以想像到佢廚房都唔會衛生得去邊。
服務員態度非常悪劣，在舊址已經差，現在環要緊差。
食物味道很好吃，也很有特色，連懷舊金錢雞都有得食。
